    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Karibian foorumi"@fi, "Karipski forum"@hr, "Caribbean Forum"@en, "Caribisch Forum"@nl, "Foro del Caribe"@es, "Karibské fórum"@cs, "Karibské fórum"@sk, "Forum caraibico"@it, "Forum des Caraïbes"@fr, "Karību valstu forums"@lv, "Det Caribiske Forum"@da, "Φόρουμ της Καραϊβικής"@el, "Fóram Mhuir Chairib"@ga, "Forum Karaibskie"@pl, "Karibisches Forum"@de, "Forumul caraib"@ro, "Cariforum"@sv, "Karibi Fórum"@hu, "Forum tal-Karibew"@mt, "Karibski forum"@sl, "Karibų forumas"@lt, "Fórum das Caraíbas"@pt, "Карибски форум"@bg, "Kariibi Foorum"@et;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Caribbean Forum (CARIFORUM) is a subgroup of African, Caribbean and Pacific Group of States and serves as a base for economic dialogue with the European Union. It was established in 1992. Its membership comprises the 15 Caribbean Community states, along with the Dominican Republic. In 2008, they signed an Economic Partnership Agreement with the European Union, though Guyana and Haiti had expressed reservations and did not attend the signing ceremony."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "CARIFORUM"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0000808"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "CARIFORUM"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>;
