    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Migration Policy Centre produces advanced policy-oriented research on global migration, asylum and mobility to serve migration governance needs at European and global levels, from developing, implementing and monitoring migration-related policies to assessing their impact on the wider economy and society."@en;
